# Screenshot directory

Drop the 5 W1 demo screenshots here before merging the proof packet PR.
Filenames must match the references in `../PROOF_PACKET.md`:

- `01-all-queue.png` — All filter, 13 cards, summary row visible
- `02-drift-filter-badges.png` — Drift filter, 4 cards with severity badges
- `03-drift-card.png` — A drift card showing workflow-aware action labels
- `04-false-positive-form.png` — False positive reason form open
- `05-action-log-mixed.png` — Action log with mixed workflow-aware verbs
